title: Def Leppard - Rock of Ages - [4K Ultra HD].mp4
description:
The 1983 Official video.

This video is in 4K 3840*2160 Ultra HD.

To play it on your 4K TV to fully enjoy and get it's full enjoyment
you will have to either play it from your computer through HDMI
or if your 4K TV has a media player you can load it on an external storage drive 
and run it through the USB port. You will be able to load this on a
flash drive stick and run it through your USB port on your 4K tv.

This is the best copy of this video I have ever seen.

And it is in 4K 2160 ultra HD.

Enjoy.


If you are a Def Leppard Fan this is a must have
